o 3 daughters.Completed application forms along with other documents must be submitted to the concerned authorities within 1 year of delivery.All those registered women labourers whose husband is taking paternity benefits from any board / dept. / corporation are not eligible.3. Eligibility Criteria for Haryana Labour Board Maternity Benefit SchemeAll the candidates must fulfill the eligibility criteria as mentioned in the table below to avail the Haryana Labour Board Maternity Benefit Scheme:-Eligibility CriteriaMembership Years / \u0938\u0926\u0938\u094d\u092f\u0924\u093e \u0935\u0930\u094d\u0937at-least 1 yearApply Frequency / \u0906\u0935\u0947\u0926\u0928 \u0915\u0940 \u0938\u0940\u092e\u093eupto 5Scheme For / \u0907\u0938 \u092f\u094b\u091c\u0928\u093e \u0915\u0947 \u0932\u093f\u090fFemaleContinue After Death / \u092e\u0943\u0924\u094d\u092f\u0941 \u0915\u0947 \u092c\u093e\u0926 \u091c\u093e\u0930\u0940NoThe total assistance under maternity benefit scheme of Haryana labour is Rs. 36,000.  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now Source / Reference Link: hrylabour.gov.in  at  "}